title: Jingle Bell Game! + Amy's Son Won't Hold Hands Anymore + Listener Questions!
itunes:title: Jingle Bell Game! + Amy's Son Won't Hold Hands Anymore + Listener Questions!
description:
Bobby plays different versions of country artists singing 'Jingle Bells' and the show members have to try and guess who's singing! Amy is distraught now that her son is growing up and not holding her hand in public anymore. Plus, Bobby and the crew answer questions from listeners!
